    <title><literal>WaitMusicOnHold()</literal></title>

    <indexterm significance="preferred">
      <primary>Dialplan Applications</primary>

      <secondary><code>WaitMusicOnHold()</code></secondary>
    </indexterm>

    <simpara>Play music-on-hold while waiting for the specified number of
    seconds.</simpara>

    <synopsis><command>WaitMusicOnHold(<replaceable>duration</replaceable>)</command></synopsis>

    <simpara>Plays music-on-hold while waiting for the specified number of
    seconds. If no hold music is available, it waits anyway, but without
    playing music.</simpara>

    <simpara>Returns 0 on completion, or -1 if the channel is hung
    up.</simpara>

    <programlisting>; 5 Minuten Wartemusik:
exten =&gt; 123,1,Answer()
exten =&gt; 123,n,WaitMusicOnHold(300)
exten =&gt; 123,n,Hangup()</programlisting>

